node.text: There was a time where I was on the WSL word tour, religiously flying and competing from country to country. Not going to lie I miss it. For the upcoming 2021 challenger series I had received a wildcard for the first four events. They went based on my 2019 ranking and I fell short due to an knee injury that year. As I am grateful for the opportunity, I’ve decided I will not compete for the 2022 champion tour. Covid has been such a crazy thing, never knowing when some random lock down may happen again😭. I also see this time as a blessing to be there for my family. But this Doesn’t mean I’m hanging up the jersey just yet. I’ll be back soon😉🤍
